  "texts": [
    "At the heart of GenAI technology is data.",
    "To detect the legal issues that the use of GenAI may cause, we looked at the model that this technology operates on: input-process-output.",
    "We classified the input (training data) using the criterion of its licit source into: open data, data provided in a voluntary way by users, consumers, professionals in their online interactions, data protected by various mechanisms (intellectual property rights, trade secrets, other means of protection), synthetic data.",
    "We found that the training data is already the 'protagonist' in a few lawsuits, mainly in US.",
    "We did not find any information on similar litigation in EU."
  ],
